OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy with occasional rain.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,8,Fcloudy with just a little light and
OL,9,Fpatchy rain. Breezy.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA mainly dry and cloudy day
OL,12,Fwith just the odd shower, although
OL,13,Fthese may become more widespread in
OL,14,Fthe west later. Some occasional
OL,15,Fbrightness in the southeast.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA
OL,18,Fchangeable, often cloudy and breezy
OL,19,Ffew days with spells of rain, but some
OL,20,Fdrier and brighter periods too,
OL,21,Fespecially in the east.
